ils with stingers like scorpions, so that with their tails they had the power to harm people for five months. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:9:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They had as their king "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or as king over them"},{"kind":"text","text":" the angel of the abyss; his name in Hebrew is Abaddon, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or Destruction"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 26:6","book":"Job","chapter":26,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 28:22","book":"Job","chapter":28,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 31:12","book":"Job","chapter":31,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 88:11","book":"Psa","chapter":88,"verse":11,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 15:11","book":"Pro","chapter":15,"verse":11,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 27:20","book":"Pro","chapter":27,"verse":20,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" and in Greek he has the name Apollyon. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Or Destroyer"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 26:6","book":"Job","chapter":26,"verse":6},{"label":"Jb 28:22","book":"Job","chapter":28,"verse":22},{"label":"Jb 31:12","book":"Job","chapter":31,"verse":12},{"label":"Ps 88:11","book":"Psa","chapter":88,"verse":11},{"label":"Pr 15:11","book":"Pro","chapter":15,"verse":11},{"label":"Pr 27:20","book":"Pro","chapter":27,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or as king over them"},{"marker":2,"text":"Or Destruction"},{"marker":3,"text":"Or Destroyer"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:9:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The first woe has passed. There are still two more woes to come after this. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 8:13","book":"Rev","chapter":8,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 11:14","book":"Rev","chapter":11,"verse":14,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rv 8:13","book":"Rev","chapter":8,"verse":13},{"label":"Rv 11:14","book":"Rev","chapter":11,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:9:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The sixth angel blew his trumpet. From the four "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss omit four"},{"kind":"text","text":" horns of the golden altar "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 39:38","book":"Exo","chapter":39,"verse":38,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 40:5","book":"Exo","chapter":40,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" that is before God, I heard a voice "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 39:38","book":"Exo","chapter":39,"verse":38},{"label":"Ex 40:5","book":"Exo","chapter":40,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss omit four"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:9:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"say to the sixth angel who had the trumpet, “Release the four angels "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 7:1–2","book":"Rev","chapter":7,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" bound at the great river Euphrates.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 16:12","book":"Rev","chapter":16,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rv 7:1–2","book":"Rev","chapter":7,"verse":1},{"label":"Rv 16:12","book":"Rev","chapter":16,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:9:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So the four angels who were prepared for the hour, day, month, and year "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 7:11","book":"Gen","chapter":7,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 25:1","book":"2Ki","chapter":25,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 39:2","book":"Jer","chapter":39,"verse":2,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 52:4","book":"Jer","chapter":52,"verse":4,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 52:12","book":"Jer","chapter":52,"verse":12,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 52:31","book":"Jer","chapter":52,"verse":31,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" were released to kill a third "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 8:7–12","book":"Rev","chapter":8,"verse":7,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" of the human race. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 7:11","book":"Gen","chapter":7,"verse":11},{"label":"2Kg 25:1","book":"2Ki","chapter":25,"verse":1},{"label":"Jr 39:2","book":"Jer","chapter":39,"verse":2},{"label":"Jr 52:4","book":"Jer","chapter":52,"verse":4},{"label":"Jr 52:12","book":"Jer","chapter":52,"verse":12},{"label":"Jr 52:31","book":"Jer","chapter":52,"verse":31},{"label":"Rv 8:7–12","book":"Rev","chapter":8,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:9:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The number of mounted troops was two hundred million; "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss read a hundred million"},{"kind":"text","text":" I heard their number. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss read a hundred million"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:9:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This is how I saw the horses and their riders in the vision: They had breastplates that were fiery red, hyacinth blue, and sulfur yellow. The heads of the horses were like the heads of lions, and from their mouths came fire, smoke, and sulfur. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 19:24","book":"Gen","chapter":19,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 29:23","book":"Deu","chapter":29,"verse":23,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 18:15","book":"Job","chapter":18,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 11:6","book":"Psa","chapter":11,"verse":6,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 34:9","book":"Isa","chapter":34,"verse":9,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 17:29","book":"Luk","chapter":17,"verse":29,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 14:10","book":"Rev","chapter":14,"verse":10,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 19:20","book":"Rev","chapter":19,"verse":20,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 20:10","book":"Rev","chap